><span><span>Para melhores informações </span></span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(246,247,248);\">0800 704 7277</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(20,24,35);font-family:Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(246,247,248);\">Ou pelo chat </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><a class=\"bbc_url\" href=\"http://www.mte-thomson.com.br/livezilla/chat.php\" rel=\"nofollow external\" title=\"Link externo\">http://www.mte-thoms...ezilla/chat.php</a></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<br>\n</br></div>"
